ang/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E6%84%9F/2021-02-24-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB421-%E7%A9%BA%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%BA%E5%BA%A6/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 Feb 2021 20:46:38 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E6%84%9F/2021-02-24-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB421-%E7%A9%BA%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%BA%E5%BA%A6/</guid><description>网络的目的：压缩时间。尽管这些系统在技术上出神入化，但核心始终是满足人类的欲望。用更少的消耗做更多的事情，在有限的时间里活得更精彩。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻420-新阶层</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E6%84%9F/2021-02-23-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB420-%E6%96%B0%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/</link><pubDate>Tue, 23 Feb 2021 21:51:10 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E6%84%9F/2021-02-23-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB420-%E6%96%B0%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/</guid><description>连接会改变事物的本质，也能让那些控制连接的人获得巨大的权力和影响力。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻419-黑客帝国</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E6%84%9F/2021-02-22-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB419-%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E5%B8%9D%E5%9B%BD/</link><pubDate>Mon, 22 Feb 2021 22:05:07 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E6%84%9F/2021-02-22-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB419-%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E5%B8%9D%E5%9B%BD/</guid><description>对一项技术的依赖性越大，研究和揭露其内部运行结构的需求就越大。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻418-连接的复杂性</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E6%84%9F/2021-02-21-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB418-%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E6%80%A7/</link><pubDate>Sun, 21 Feb 2021 23:27:46 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E6%84%9F/2021-02-21-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB418-%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E6%80%A7/</guid><description>正如你的预想，系统越复杂，产生的交互作用越多，也意味着前方的路将比我们以前面对的更难走、更具挑战性。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻417-连接之门</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E6%84%9F/2021-02-20-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB417-%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%A8/</link><pubDate>Sat, 20 Feb 2021 21:32:20 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E6%84%9F/2021-02-20-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB417-%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%A8/</guid><description>在连接时代，力量融入网络会产生一种全新的布局。分散与集中就是网络力量的本质，既井然有序又混乱无序，既有益又有害。</description></item></channel></rss>